reviewText: This was an informative DVD about the Mayans and their prophesies (obviously). There was a shift in 2012, and it was foretold in their calendar, which is something we should always reference as it is a wonderful guide.
I think that December 21'st 2012 was not mean as the end of days but rather a fresh start, maybe even a reset button for humanity. That's what I took away from this cool release.

Well, obviously the world did not come to an end in 2012, but this video is not about that. It is about a spiritual shift. I do believe this has happened. Check out this video and you will see what I'm talking about.
